nodes.title: Instructions for use
widgets_values:
ai virtual photography workflow v2.4.240504
Specially built for photography enthusiasts, it generates model photos, posture control, and high-definition restoration
Note: The XL model used this time has removed the inpainting model used in the 1.5 version of the image expansion. 

Update content:
1. Adapted to the latest IPAdapter plus, which can be generated according to the specified character's face and painting style
2. Integration of checkpoints and lora loader for easy expansion
3. Skeleton diagram node updated to editable skeleton diagram
 n4. New style selector
5. Delete tiled zoom (the effect is not ideal and drag speed)
6. Delete ipadapter face changing (adapted to the new version)

Instructions for use:
Order according to the grouping number when running for the first time Make settings and upload the corresponding pictures. If you do not upload pictures, be sure to disable the grouping; 
S class groups are system modules, including common settings, such as: sampler, seed, number of steps, CFG, redraw amplitude, amplification factor, unified Settings, effective for adoption and subsequent high-definition amplification; 
U-category is grouped into high-definition repair modules, three of which can be selected at will, all have certain repair capabilities, and can be disabled or enabled according to needs. 


----------------------------------------------- 

WeChat: gary1780
QQ group: 647564984 (password: ai)
Douyin: 963053212
Xiaohongshu/Bilibili: Lepi ai

此处需要选择带inpainting能力的大 model才能达到最好效果

注意，此处无需与前面的 model版本保持一致

如果想对upscale 的图进行扩图操作，需要将输入的image节点与高清upscale 输出节点连接。

此扩图功能可独立使用，只需要将image switch设置为【false】，就能单独上传图片进行扩图。默认为【true】将生成的图片进行扩展。

1、基础文生图，主要根据文本输入来完成，输入 1，此时生成人物姿态由提示词控制

2、在文生图基础上，由骨架图控制生成人物姿态，输入 2

文生图生成 的随机性更大，指定姿态之后会固定人物姿态，而且还能有效控制，避免出现多手多脚的情况

1、上传人物照片，提取人物姿态,输入 1

2、已有骨架图或自定义骨架图，输入 2

当右侧condition输入为 1 时，人物姿态设置不生效，即不受控。


同时自动获取图片分辨率,并以该分辨率作为生成图片尺寸

如大 model为XL,则此处预处理器选择对应XL版本

首次运行，两个上传图片的节点均不能为空。

自定义尺寸
参数说明：
可在aspect_ratio中按宽高比设置，也可以选择custom后自行定义宽高；
swap_dimensions为宽高转换
